<h2 id="section-top">Weight loss services</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=2012">Imperial College Healthcare NHS Trust</a>
</p>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContente282b18096b4487ba07f8b736e831a46">
</div>
<p>Our weight loss (bariatric) service based at St Mary’s Hospital in London, is  known as the Imperial Weight Centre. We provide a comprehensive surgical and  medical service for patients from across the UK who are overweight, have medical  problems and need to lose weight to improve their health. Our primary objective  is to make our patients healthy.</p>
<p>We are recognised as an international centre for bariatric surgery and as  part of the UK’s first Academic Health Science Centre (AHSC), provide training  for other health care professionals in partnership with Imperial College  London.</p>
<p>The Imperial Weight Centre is one of very few centres accredited as an  International Centre of Excellence (ICE) for bariatric surgery, and was the  first in the UK to be awarded this accreditation.</p>
<p>Our bariatric unit is based in the new Surgical Innovation Centre in the  Paterson wing at St Mary’s hospital. The unit encompasses the bariaric  outpatient clinics, inpatient ward and operating theatres - all inside one  building.</p>
<p>The operations that we perform are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Gastric bypass </li>
<li>Sleeve gastrectomy </li>
<li>Gastric band </li>
</ul>
<p>Most surgery is performed laparascopically.</p>
<p>Visit our website (<a href="http://www.imperial.nhs.uk/">www.imperial.nhs.uk</a>) to find out more  information about our <a href="http://www.imperial.nhs.uk/services/weightloss/index.htm">weight loss service</a>.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
